data.title: SoulCycle Instructor
data.meta_description: SoulCycle has revolutionized indoor cycling and taken the world of fitness by storm. 45 minutes to take your journey. Change your body. Find your SOUL
data.text:
What's your Soul Story?

Charilyn brings her dance background and passion for music to Soul. In her class you will be able to experience music with your entire body and allow the rhythm to propel you forward. Finding motivation from every beat, Charilyn will guide you through a journey to rediscovery of yourself.
